059  public ReceiptTemplatePayload(String recipientName, String orderNumber, String currency, String paymentMethod, ReceiptSummary summary) {
060    this.recipientName = recipientName;
061    this.orderNumber = orderNumber;
062    this.currency = currency;
063    this.paymentMethod = paymentMethod;
064    this.summary = summary;
065    setTemplateType("receipt");
066  }
